		<article>	
			<h2>What is Membery?</h2>
			<h3>Who is membery for?</h3>
			<p>Regardless whether it is an organisation with complicated structures with thousands of members or small & medium sport's club, we've covered it all.
			Membery is suitable for Non-Government Organization, Unions, Associations Sport & Hobbies organisations and other member based institutions.
			Central management organizations may find Membery very helpful to execute various management tasks and communicational activities in a simple and effective way.</p>

			<h3>What is Membery?</h3>
			<p>Membery is an online software solution for various types of organisations to help them with effective coordination, management and organisation their members. 
			Our core features are as following: Information distribution, tracking payments, simplifying members database or execution of specific tasks within the organization.
			Membery provides several pre-set functionalities that are supporting standard processes in organization. Nonetheless, our solution is fully customized with features that are easy to manage and enable you to provide various organisational activities effectively.</p>
		</article>
